flowchart TD
    A[Email arrives at feedback@] --> B{Subject starts with [feedback]?}
    B -- no --> X1[Drop to /dev/null]
    B -- yes --> C[Read email body]
    C --> D[Ollama ask: triage prompt]
    D --> E{Parse JSON ok?}
    E -- no --> X2[Log to audit/failures.jsonl]
    E -- yes --> F{Urgency?}
    F -- high --> G[Post to #feedback-triage with [urgent] + @bootcamp-pm]
    F -- medium --> H[Post to #feedback-triage]
    F -- low --> I[Append to data/feedback-queue.jsonl]
    G --> J[Append to audit/feedback.jsonl]
    H --> J
    I --> J
    J --> K[Done]
